<html lang="en">
<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8" />
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0" />
  <title>Plan Your Trip | Dark Destinations</title>
  <link rel="stylesheet" href="/css/style.css">
  <link rel="stylesheet" href="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/bootstrap@5.3.5/dist/css/bootstrap.min.css">

  <link rel="stylesheet" href="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/bootstrap@5.3.5/dist/css/bootstrap.min.css" />
  <link rel="stylesheet" href="https://cdnjs.cloudflare.com/ajax/libs/font-awesome/6.7.2/css/all.min.css" />
  <link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Vollkorn:wght@600&family=Prompt&display=swap" rel="stylesheet">
  
  
  <link rel="preconnect" href="https://fonts.googleapis.com">
  <link rel="preconnect" href="https://fonts.gstatic.com" crossorigin>
  <link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Plus+Jakarta+Sans&family=Exile&family=Tagesschrift&family=EB+Garamond&display=swap" rel="stylesheet">

  <link rel="preconnect" href="https://fonts.googleapis.com">
<link rel="preconnect" href="https://fonts.gstatic.com" crossorigin>
<link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Akaya+Kanadaka&family=Averia+Libre:ital,wght@0,300;0,400;0,700;1,300;1,400;1,700&family=Creepster&family=Diplomata&family=EB+Garamond:ital,wght@0,400..800;1,400..800&display=swap" rel="stylesheet">
  <style>
    body {
      /* margin: 0; */
      /* background: linear-gradient(to right, #111, #1f1f1f); */
      color: #f8f8f8;
      /* font-family: 'Prompt', sans-serif; */
    }

    header {
      background: #000;
      padding: 3rem 1rem;
      text-align: center;
      border-bottom: 3px solid #ff3333;
    }

    header h1 {
      font-family: 'Vollkorn', serif;
      font-size: 3rem;
      color: #ff3333;
    }

    header p {
      font-size: 1.2rem;
      color: #ccc;
    }

    .trip-section {
      max-width: 1100px;
      margin: auto;
      padding: 4rem 2rem;
    }

    .trip-step {
      margin-bottom: 3rem;
      border-left: 4px solid #ff3333;
      padding-left: 1.5rem;
    }

    .trip-step h3 {
      color: #ff3333;
      font-weight: 600;
      margin-bottom: 0.8rem;
    }

    .trip-step p {
      color: #bbb;
      line-height: 1.6rem;
    }

    .cta-box {
      text-align: center;
      background: #141414;
      padding: 2.5rem;
      border-radius: 15px;
      /* box-shadow: 0 0 20px rgba(255, 100, 60, 0.1); */
    }

    .cta-box h4 {
      color: #fff;
      margin-bottom: 1.8rem;
    }

    .cta-box a {
      text-decoration: none;
      background: #f41c1c;
      color: white;
      padding: 0.8rem 1.6rem;
      border-radius: 30px;
      transition: background 0.3s ease;
    }

    .cta-box a:hover {
      background: #810202;
    }
  </style>
</head>
<body>
    <%- include("../includes/navbar.ejs") %>
  <header>
    <h1>Plan Your Trip</h1>
    <p>Everything you need to prepare for your next haunted journey.</p>
  </header>

  <section class="trip-section">
    <div class="trip-step">
      <h3>1. Choose Your Destination</h3>
      <p>Explore our eerie catalog of haunted locations. From cursed castles to abandoned hospitals, there's a thrill for every brave heart.</p>
    </div>

    <div class="trip-step">
      <h3>2. Book Safely</h3>
      <p>Use our secure booking system to reserve your spot. Our hosts ensure your stay is spooky, yet safe.</p>
    </div>

    <div class="trip-step">
      <h3>3. Pack Accordingly</h3>
      <p>Flashlights, EMF detectors, and a brave heart — don’t forget the essentials. Our checklists help you gear up for the unknown.</p>
    </div>

    <div class="trip-step">
      <h3>4. Get Insider Tips</h3>
      <p>Read reviews and haunted travel guides from fellow explorers. Learn when to go, what to expect, and what to avoid.</p>
    </div>

    <div class="trip-step">
      <h3>5. Share Your Experience</h3>
      <p>After your trip, come back and share your story. Who knows — your ghost story might inspire the next visitor.</p>
    </div>

    <div class="cta-box">
      <h4>Ready to face the unknown?</h4>
      <a href="/home/listings">Start Exploring</a>
    </div>
  </section>

<%- include("../includes/footer.ejs") %>

  <script src="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/bootstrap@5.3.5/dist/js/bootstrap.bundle.min.js"></script>
  <script src="/js/script.js"></script>
</body>
</html>
